{"tid":2128087,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美通過185億軍售案　協助智利現代化F-16機隊...無線電系統大提升","createTime":"2020-07-27T17:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T18:21:37.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c01c80926b2c2b5b501c93a085f7af399af4e32","tid":2128087,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5033/d5033484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5033%2Fd5033484.jpg&h=67a42802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智利國際航空航天展覽會（FIDAE）中亮相的F-16。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n記者楊庭蒝／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院日前向批准了智利政府關於升級F-16的軍售案，合約價值高達6.34億美元（約台幣185億元），內含多款現代化裝備，此外，智利可能進一步購買數架新型的F-16，以提高智利應對當前和未來威脅的能力。<br />\n<br />\n根據《美國國防新聞週刊》報導，在此軍售案當中，包括了19個聯合頭盔瞄準系統（Joint Helmet Mounted Cueing System, JHMCS）、6個MK-82（500 LB）通用炸彈、2個MXU-650KB機翼組、44個LN-260嵌入式GPS / INS和49個聯合戰術無線電系統（JTRS）。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，智利目前擁有44架得F-16戰機，其中包刮在2000年初期購買的10架F-16C / D Block 50。<br />\n<br />\n此外，在智利原的F-16當中，將針對航空電子設備和軟體、IFF天線耦合器套件等其他安全通訊設備進行升級，此項升級涉及44架F-16戰機。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防安全合作局（DSCA）聲明指出，擬議中將通過出售F-16戰機，提升智利實現軍隊現代化的目標，以應對當前與未來面對威脅的能力，這將使智利能夠維護主權和國土，並增強與美國和其他合作夥伴的合作。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200728/1770715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200728%2F1770715.htm&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=41cfc25f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200728/1770715.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9803d5cf3529e4c6d9c42bf0768213e45042a0e7","tid":2128087,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"美國成功拉攏南美智利了"},{"pid":"0768636ffeda4f2fc1677af716cad46da48c6da9","tid":2128087,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9803d5cf3529e4c6d9c42bf0768213e45042a0e7","tid":2128087,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"美國成功拉攏南美智利了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"咁大個美國係隔離除左D獨裁國家, 敢痴中國咩"},{"pid":"f0407babdd5b56a9b7b94056958c43a5affd36ec","tid":2128087,"uid":27688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"智利同巴西都唔好用華為吧"},{"pid":"f9af0763ae1a06d20daec483c72e6e6d2c5cbfbb","tid":2128087,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"智利國土南北長達4000多公里，單引擎既F-16真係夠用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係因為東面西面國家都太廢防都唔洗防"}]}